import {
    ArcSeries, AreaSeries,
    ContourSeries, HeatmapSeries, HexbinSeries,
    HorizontalGridLines, LabelSeries, LineMarkSeries,
    LineSeries,
    MarkSeries,
    VerticalBarSeries,
    XAxis,
    XYPlot,
    YAxis
} from "react-vis";

let data = [
    {x: 1, y: 100},
    {x: 2, y: 90},
    {x: 3, y: 80},
    {x: 4, y: 70},
    {x: 5, y: 60},
    {x: 6, y: 50},
    {x: 7, y: 70},
    {x: 8, y: 80},
    {x: 9, y: 90},
    {x: 10, y: 100},
    {x: 11, y: 90},
    {x: 12, y: 50},
]

export const Graph = () => {
    return (
        <XYPlot
            width={1500}
            height={300}
            colorType="linear"
            stroke="red"
        >
            <HorizontalGridLines/>
            <LineMarkSeries data={data} curve={'curveMonotoneX'} />
            <XAxis/>
            <YAxis/>
        </XYPlot>
    )
}
